{
  "texts": [
    "We conducted matched guise probing in two settings.",
    "In the first setting, the texts in T a and T s formed pairs expressing the same underlying meaning, that is, the i-th text in T a (for example, 'I be so happy when I wake up from a bad dream cus they be feelin too real') matches the i-th text in T s (for example, 'I am so happy when I wake up from a bad dream because they feel too real').",
    "For this setting, we used the dataset from ref.",
    "87, which contains 2,019 AAE tweets together with their SAE translations.",
    "In the second setting, the texts in T a and T s did not form pairs, so they were independent texts in AAE and SAE."
  ]
}